\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3612923 AH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14316909\charrsid8657389 I was born in - {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}North London{\*\xmlclose} - only Clapton not so here, in 
